CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 1, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "The Aniketos - The Aniketos carried out tradition in grand style at the formal held at the Loendi recently, which brought out the cream of the younger set. The Aniketos' doings augmented Frog Week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Aniketos club, possibly including Mozelle Thompson and June Tansimore standing on left, William Marable standing on right, and possibly Richard Britton squatting on right, posed during formal in Loendi Club
